These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, july, november, february, march
City: hamburg, paris, colone, rome, london
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
7. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Birthday   | july | november | april | march | february |
| City   | london    | hamburg | colone     | rome       | paris  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, december, june, february, may
5 different games are played: poker, scrabble, billiard, go, whist
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is the person playing billiard##1
6. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Birthday      | december | june | august | february | may |
| Game   | billiard  | go   | poker       | scrabble    | whist   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
House: art-deco, tower, victorian, cottage, modern
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: snowboarding, weightlifting, cycling, basketball, skiing
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the victorian house is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the tower house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| House        | victorian | cottage | tower | art-deco | modern |
| Sport   | weightlifting  | snowboarding      | skiing | cycling | basketball      |

