.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: british, indian, japanese, canadian, argentine
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, subway, snowmobile, taxi, bike
1. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the japanese is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the indian is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
5. the british is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Nationality   | canadian    | british        | japanese | indian | argentine |
| Transport     | train | taxi | bike  | subway   | snowmobile |

