.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
5 different pets are kept: horse, dog, snake, rat, goat
There are 5 different favourite colors: emerald, light-blue, orange, ivory, lilac
1. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is the owner of the goat##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the person who likes orange is in the middle##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
6. the person who likes lilac is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Pet    | snake   | horse     | dog   | rat         | goat |
| Color   | emerald | ivory | orange | lilac | light-blue     |

