.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
House: gothic-revival, futuristic, craftsman, palace, cottage
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, sports, mystery, disaster, western
1. the person watching disaster movies is in the middle##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is the craftsman house##1
5. the cottage house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| House       | palace   | craftsman   | futuristic | cottage | gothic-revival |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | mystery | disaster   | western | animation       |

