.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
There 5 different types of food: cranberry, blueberry, radish, garlic, peach
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, snowmobile, scooter, bike
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the boat is the person eating cranberry##1
3. the person eating peach is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
5. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Food     | blueberry   | radish  | peach      | cranberry | garlic     |
| Transport   | scooter | snowmobile | bus | boat   | bike |

