.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
House: cottage, palace, tower, wooden, gothic-revival
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, gardening, sudoku, hiking, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the cottage house is on the right of the palace house##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| House     | palace | cottage       | gothic-revival | wooden | tower    |
| Hobby   | hiking   | card-games | sudoku  | gardening     | dancing |

