.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, tulip, iris, lily, daffodil
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, sprite, juice, iced-tea
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
4. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person who growslily is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Flower         | lily | amaryllis | iris | daffodil | tulip |
| Beverage   | sprite       | juice   | iced-tea         | almond-milk   | soy-milk   |

