.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, traveling, sudoku, dancing, woodworking
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, prince, aristoff, dannemann, swisher
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the prince-smoker is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the prince-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the game-smoker##1
7. the swisher-smoker is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Hobby   | dancing | hiking  | sudoku | traveling | woodworking |
| Cigar    | prince    | dannemann | swisher   | game       | aristoff        |

