.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, aristoff, dunhill, old-henry, baccarat
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, sprite, cola, water
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is the person drinking water##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Cigar    | pall-mall | old-henry          | dunhill    | baccarat | aristoff  |
| Beverage   | sprite  | water | almond-milk | cola | hot-chocolate |

