3. the person who likes ebony is the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Sport   | swimming | surfing      | rowing | baseball | water-polo |
| Color     | chestnut  | ebony | ivory     | amber     | blood-red  |

