.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, biathlon, baseball, rugby, ice-hockey
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, tram, roller, bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Sport           | rugby     | ice-hockey | lacrosse | baseball  | biathlon |
| Transport   | airplane | helicopter               | tram     | roller | bike |

