4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
6. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |      5      |
| City    | hannover   | venice | miami      | marseilles | san-francisco        |
| Game   | billiard | whist     | backgammon | snooker | monopoly |

