4. the cape-cod house is the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
6. the ranch-style house is the owner of the snake##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
| House   | cape-cod   | art-deco    | tower | ranch-style   | gothic-revival |
| Pet     | dog | hedgehog | chinchilla | snake | fish    |

