.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: mauve, green, purple, azure, chestnut
The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, hiking, rock-climbing, puzzles, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who likes azure##1
5. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
7. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Color   | chestnut     | purple       | mauve     | green  | azure  |
| Hobby      | puzzles | reading | hiking | gardening | rock-climbing |

