.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike, tram, train, motorbike
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, lemonade, coffee, sprite
1. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Transport   | bike | motorbike | tram | snowmobile | train |
| Beverage           | sprite | coffee  | cola    | tea  | lemonade   |

 